            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 compensate-right">
                    <img src="https://d1d9oqfe9g83w6.cloudfront.net/assets1485960229/img/img-12.jpg" alt="book auto transport order" width="100%">
                </div>
                
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="offset">
                        <h3>Book your Order</h3>
                        <p>Online or over the phone, select a payment option, and place a reservation.</p>
                        <dl>
                            <dt><a href="how-it-works#payment" data-toggle="collapse">Multiple payment methods</a></dt>
                            <dd class="collapse" id="payment">
                                <ul>
                                    <li>“Cash Rate Discount”. Pay the driver in cash, money order, or cashiers check. A deposit will be charged at the time of booking or when a driver has been assigned.</li>
                                    <li>Billing. Pay the full amount on a credit card or through PayPal.</li>
                                </ul>
                            </dd>
                        
                            <dt><a href="how-it-works#edit-order" data-toggle="collapse">Edit your order [anytime]</a></dt>
                            <dd class="collapse" id="edit-order">Missing info? No problem, update it when you have it.</dd>
                        
                            <dt><a href="how-it-works#support" data-toggle="collapse">365 days/7days a week support</a></dt>
                            <dd class="collapse" id="support">Available via phone, chat, and email. We’re here for you, every step of the way.</dd>
                        </dl>
                        
                        <a href="transport-tips.1#payment" class="btn btn-default btn-lg">Read more <i class="fa fa-chevron-right fa-fw"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
                
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 col-md-push-6 compensate-left">
