                </div>
                
                <div class="col-md-6 col-md-pull-6">
                    <div class="offset">
                        <h3>Tracking and Updates</h3>
                        <p>Dates for pickup and delivery are provided when a carrier has been dispatched.</p>
                        <dl>
                            <dt><a href="how-it-works#get-notified" data-toggle="collapse">Get notified when a trucker is assigned</a></dt>
                            <dd class="collapse" id="get-notified">Email and courtesy calls for every step of your order.</dd>
                        
                            <dt><a href="how-it-works#transit-time" data-toggle="collapse">Transit time</a></dt>
                            <dd class="collapse" id="transit-time">May be affected by weather, traffic, and scheduling. We keep you up to date on your shipment’s progress.</dd>
                        
                            <dt><a href="how-it-works#monitoring" data-toggle="collapse">Montway shipment monitoring</a></dt>
                            <dd class="collapse" id="monitoring">Experienced Car Shipping Advisors oversee your order from the moment it’s placed, to when it’s delivered.</dd>
                        </dl>
                        
                        <a href="contact-us" class="btn btn-default btn-lg">Contact us <i class="fa fa-chevron-right fa-fw"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
                
