                </div>
                
                <div class="col-md-6">
                    <div class="offset">
                        <h3>Pickup and Delivery</h3>
                        <p>Door to door transportation <span class="inline-help" data-toggle="popover" data-placement="top" data-trigger="hover" data-content="Truck delivery may be restricted in residential areas. In this case, the trucker will meet you at the nearest accessible location.">?</span></p>
                        <dl>
                            <dt><a href="how-it-works#notice" data-toggle="collapse">Advanced notice for pickup and delivery</a></dt>
                            <dd class="collapse" id="notice">Coordinate with the trucker for convenient scheduling.</dd>
                        
                            <dt><a href="how-it-works#carrier-information" data-toggle="collapse">Trucker/carrier information</a></dt>
                            <dd class="collapse" id="carrier-information">We will provide you the contact information of the trucker and their company once they have been assigned.</dd>
                        
                            <dt><a href="how-it-works#inspection" data-toggle="collapse">Vehicle inspection</a></dt>
                            <dd class="collapse" id="inspection">Inspect the condition of the vehicle prior to releasing and accepting your shipment with the trucker. If there is an issue, please give us a call.</dd>
                        </dl>
                        
